7 COMMITTEE SUBSTITUTE
8 An Act relating to motor vehicles; amending 22 O.S.
2021, Section 1115.1A, as last amended by Section 1,
9 Chapter 57, O.S.L. 2024 (22 O.S. Supp. 2025, Section
1115.1A), which relates to release on personal
10 recognizance for traffic violation; adding certain
exception; amending 47 O.S. 2021, Sections 6-111, as
11 last amended by Section 2, Chapter 310, O.S.L. 2025,
3, Chapter 310, O.S.L. 2025, and 4, Chapter 310,
12 O.S.L. 2025 (47 O.S. Supp. 2025, Sections 6-111, 6-
126.1, and 6-126.2), which relate to motor vehicle
13 enforcement; removing certain violations; requiring
persons operating a commercial motor vehicle to
14 possess certain identification; requiring certain
additional identification in certain circumstance;
15 providing for certain offense; prescribing certain
enforcement standards; providing for certain
16 violation; defining term; creating certain
administrative fine for certain offenses; providing
17 for certain hearing; amending 47 O.S. 2021, Section
955, as amended by Section 12, Chapter 228, O.S.L.
18 2022 (47 O.S. Supp. 2025, Section 955), which relates
to towing of vehicles from roadway; allowing for
19 certain vehicles when certain persons are placed
under custodial arrest; updating statutory
20 references; providing for codification; and declaring
an emergency.
